Package org.apache.sling.scripting.sightly.impl.parser.expr.generated

Interface SightlyParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
SightlyParserBaseListener
public interface SightlyParserListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by SightlyParser.
